Catherine KELLY, Appellant, v. Louis E. RIECK, Trustee of VEELOCK MFG. CO., et al. No. 6885. Circuit Court of Appeals, Third Circuit. Jan. 11, 1939. James R. Wilson, William J. Wilson, and William F. Zinger, all of Philadelphia, Pa., for appellant. Frank J. Bowden, of Philadelphia, Pa., for appellees.

Before BIGGS, MARIS, and CLARK, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Order affirmed upon the opinion of Judge Dickinson, In re Veelock Mfg. Co., 26 F.Supp. 110.
